    public class ElevationSelector
extends BaseSelector
implements ElevationSelectorIF
    An implementation of ElevationSelectorIF which presents the available elevations as a drop down list. In the case where we have a continuous depth axis, this will still be the case, but ranges will be generated, and the values shown will be the centre points of these ranges. The protocol for continuous vertical axes is more flexible, but in practice this is sufficient
    Author:
    Guy Griffiths
